Package: nflytics
Title: Bayesian NFL Team Strength and Forecasting Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tyler", "Pollard", email = "TylerPollard410@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for preparing play-level and game-level NFL data, fitting latent team
    strength state-space models in Stan, and generating posterior summaries, predictions,
    and diagnostics similar to the workflows in 'brms', 'rstanarm', and 'footBayes'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
